# Plug-in Interfaces тАФ CRI ┬╖ CNI ┬╖ CSI

Small core тЖТ three plug-in seams.

## CRI тАФ Container Runtime

> gRPC kubelet тЖТ runtime. `RuntimeService` (lifecycle) + `ImageService` (images). **One per node** тАФ containerd / CRI-O.

## CNI тАФ Container Network

> JSON-over-stdin. On new Pod netns: **(1)** allocate Pod IP ┬╖ **(2)** program routing (Pods, Services, internet) ┬╖ **(3)** return IP.

- **Calico ┬╖ Cilium ┬╖ Flannel ┬╖ AWS VPC ┬╖ Azure** тАФ differ in encap (VXLAN / L3 / **eBPF**), NetworkPolicy, perf.
- `kind` тЖТ `kindnet`.

## CSI тАФ Container Storage

> gRPC to backends (notebook 06). One driver per backend.

## The point

> K8s = **orchestration**; the *doing* is **delegated**. Same logic on a Pi (k3s) or 1000-node EKS.
